query:
-- Buscar romaneios ativos
SELECT 
  sm.id as romaneioId,
  sm.manifestNumber,
  sm.status as statusRomaneio,
  sm.createdAt,
  COUNT(DISTINCT smi.pickingOrderId) as totalPedidos
FROM shipmentManifests sm
LEFT JOIN shipmentManifestItems smi ON sm.id = smi.manifestId
WHERE sm.status IN ('pending', 'in_progress', 'loaded')
GROUP BY sm.id, sm.manifestNumber, sm.status, sm.createdAt
ORDER BY sm.createdAt DESC;
